Name: CAPACITY MAXIMUM
Explanation: THE MAXIMUM CAPACITY KNOWN. WHEN CAPACITY IS REPRESENTED AS A RANGE, THIS FIELD INDICATES THE MAXIMUM ACTUAL OR POTENTIAL ABILITY TO DO SOMETHING.

Name: STORAGE CAPACITY
Explanation: THE ACTUAL OR POTENTIAL ABILITY TO STORE SOMETHING.

Name: PRODUCTION CAPACITY
Explanation: THE ACTUAL OR POTENTIAL ABILITY TO PRODUCE SOMETHING.
